Title: The thermal energy of a scalar field in a one-dimensional compact space
Authors: E. Elizalde, A. C. Tort
Comments: 13 pages, LaTeX, no figures
Subj-class: High Energy Physics - Theory; Mathematical Physics
Journal-ref: Phys.Rev. D66 (2002) 045033
\\
  We discuss some controverted aspects of the evaluation of the thermal energy
of a scalar field in a one-dimensional compact space. The calculations are
carried out using a generalised zeta function approach.
